        <h2 class="tourtitle"> Tour Packages </h2>

        <div class="packagesize">
            <div class="homepackage">
                <h2 class="homepackagetitle">Adventure Tours</h2>
    
                <p class="textdes"> Adventure tours are designed for thrill-seekers and adrenaline junkies who seek
                    excitement and challenges during their travels. These packages often include activities such
                    as hiking, mountain biking, whitewater rafting, rock climbing, zip-lining, and wildlife safaris.
                    Adventure tours are typically suited for individuals or groups with a spirit of adventure and a
                    desire to explore rugged landscapes and remote destinations.
                </p>

                <button class="homepackbtn"> <a class="homepacklnk" href="#">SEEMORE..</a></button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="homepackage">
                <h2 class="homepackagetitle">Cultural Tours</h2>
    
                <p class="textdes"> Cultural tours focus on immersing travelers in the rich heritage, history, and
                    traditions of a particular region or country. These packages often include visits to historical
                    sites, museums, art galleries, religious monuments, local markets, and traditional performances.
                    Travelers have the opportunity to learn about the customs, cuisine, language, and lifestyle of
                    the local people, gaining a deeper understanding of their culture.
                </p>

                <button class="homepackbtn"> <a class="homepacklnk" href="#">SEEMORE..</a></button>

            </div>
    
            <div class="homepackage">
                <h2 class="homepackagetitle">Eco-Tours</h2>
    
                <p class="textdes">  Eco-tours focus on responsible and sustainable travel practices, emphasizing
                    conservation, environmental awareness, and community engagement. These packages offer opportunities
                    to explore natural landscapes, wildlife habitats, and eco-friendly initiatives while minimizing
                    the impact on the environment.
                </p>

                <button class="homepackbtn"> <a class="homepacklnk" href="#">SEEMORE..</a></button>

            </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="tourtitle"> Tour Guides </h2>
        
        <div class="packagesize">
            <div class="homepackage">
                <h2 class="homepackagetitle">Historical Tour Guides</h2>
    
                <p class="textdes"> These guides specialize in providing insights into the history of a particular
                    location. They often have extensive knowledge of historical events, landmarks, architecture, and
                    cultural heritage. Historical tour guides may lead visitors through museums, ancient ruins,
                    historic neighborhoods, or significant landmarks, providing context and anecdotes that bring
                    the past to life.
                </p>

                <button class="homepackbtn"> <a class="homepacklnk" href="#">SEEMORE..</a></button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="homepackage">
                <h2 class="homepackagetitle">Specialized Interest Guides</h2>
    
                <p class="textdes"> Specialized interest guides cater to niche interests and hobbies, providing
                    tailored experiences for specific groups of travelers. Examples include art guides who lead
                    tours of museums and galleries, wine guides who organize vineyard tours and wine tastings,
                    photography guides who help capture the best shots of scenic locations, and ghost tour guides
                    who delve into local legends and haunted sites.
                </p>

                <button class="homepackbtn"> <a class="homepacklnk" href="#">SEEMORE..</a></button>

            </div>
    
            <div class="homepackage">
                <h2 class="homepackagetitle">Ecotourism Guides</h2>
    
                <p class="textdes">  Ecotourism guides specialize in promoting sustainable travel practices and
                    educating visitors about environmental conservation. They lead tours to natural habitats such
                    as rainforests, coral reefs, national parks, and wildlife sanctuaries, emphasizing the 
                    importance of preserving these ecosystems. Ecotourism guides often provide information on
                    local flora and fauna, ecological processes, and conservation efforts, encouraging travelers
                    to minimize their environmental impact and support conservation initiatives.
                </p>

                <button class="homepackbtn"> <a class="homepacklnk" href="#">SEEMORE..</a></button>

            </div>
